  <script>
   $(document).ready(function(){(function($,window,document,undefined){'use strict';var jRange=function(){return this.init.apply(this,arguments);};jRange.prototype={defaults:{onstatechange:function(){},ondragend:function(){},onbarclicked:function(){},isRange:false,showLabels:true,showScale:true,step:1,format:'%s',theme:'theme-green',width:300,disable:false,snap:false},template:'<div class="priceslider-container">\
   <div class="back-bar">\
                <div class="selected-bar"></div>\
                <div class="pointer low"></div><div class="pointer-label low">123456</div>\
                <div class="pointer high"></div><div class="pointer-label high">456789</div>\
                <div class="clickable-dummy"></div>\
            </div>\
            <div class="scale"></div>\
  </div>',init:function(node,options){this.options=$.extend({},this.defaults,options);this.inputNode=$(node);this.options.value=this.inputNode.val()||(this.options.isRange?this.options.from+','+this.options.from:''+this.options.from);this.domNode=$(this.template);this.domNode.addClass(this.options.theme);this.inputNode.after(this.domNode);this.domNode.on('change',this.onChange);this.pointers=$('.pointer',this.domNode);this.lowPointer=this.pointers.first();this.highPointer=this.pointers.last();this.labels=$('.pointer-label',this.domNode);this.lowLabel=this.labels.first();this.highLabel=this.labels.last();this.scale=$('.scale',this.domNode);this.bar=$('.selected-bar',this.domNode);this.clickableBar=this.domNode.find('.clickable-dummy');this.interval=this.options.to-this.options.from;this.render();},render:function(){if(this.inputNode.width()===0&&!this.options.width){console.log('jRange : no width found, returning');return;}else{this.options.width=this.options.width||this.inputNode.width();this.domNode.width(this.options.width);this.inputNode.hide();}
if(this.isSingle()){this.lowPointer.hide();this.lowLabel.hide();}
if(!this.options.showLabels){this.labels.hide();}
this.attachEvents();if(this.options.showScale){this.renderScale();}
this.setValue(this.options.value);},isSingle:function(){if(typeof(this.options.value)==='number'){return true;}
return(this.options.value.indexOf(',')!==-1||this.options.isRange)?false:true;},attachEvents:function(){this.clickableBar.click($.proxy(this.barClicked,this));this.pointers.on('mousedown touchstart',$.proxy(this.onDragStart,this));this.pointers.bind('dragstart',function(event){event.preventDefault();});},onDragStart:function(e){if(this.options.disable||(e.type==='mousedown'&&e.which!==1)){return;}
e.stopPropagation();e.preventDefault();var pointer=$(e.target);this.pointers.removeClass('last-active');pointer.addClass('focused last-active');this[(pointer.hasClass('low')?'low':'high')+'Label'].addClass('focused');$(document).on('mousemove.slider touchmove.slider',$.proxy(this.onDrag,this,pointer));$(document).on('mouseup.slider touchend.slider touchcancel.slider',$.proxy(this.onDragEnd,this));},onDrag:function(pointer,e){e.stopPropagation();e.preventDefault();if(e.originalEvent.touches&&e.originalEvent.touches.length){e=e.originalEvent.touches[0];}else if(e.originalEvent.changedTouches&&e.originalEvent.changedTouches.length){e=e.originalEvent.changedTouches[0];}
var position=e.clientX-this.domNode.offset().left;this.domNode.trigger('change',[this,pointer,position]);},onDragEnd:function(e){this.pointers.removeClass('focused').trigger('rangeslideend');this.labels.removeClass('focused');$(document).off('.slider');this.options.ondragend.call(this,this.options.value);},barClicked:function(e){if(this.options.disable)return;var x=e.pageX-this.clickableBar.offset().left;if(this.isSingle())
this.setPosition(this.pointers.last(),x,true,true);else{var firstLeft=Math.abs(parseFloat(this.pointers.first().css('left'),10)),firstHalfWidth=this.pointers.first().width()/2,lastLeft=Math.abs(parseFloat(this.pointers.last().css('left'),10)),lastHalfWidth=this.pointers.first().width()/2,leftSide=Math.abs(firstLeft-x+firstHalfWidth),rightSide=Math.abs(lastLeft-x+lastHalfWidth),pointer;if(leftSide==rightSide){pointer=x<firstLeft?this.pointers.first():this.pointers.last();}else{pointer=leftSide<rightSide?this.pointers.first():this.pointers.last();}
this.setPosition(pointer,x,true,true);}
this.options.onbarclicked.call(this,this.options.value);},onChange:function(e,self,pointer,position){var min,max;min=0;max=self.domNode.width();if(!self.isSingle()){min=pointer.hasClass('high')?parseFloat(self.lowPointer.css("left"))+(self.lowPointer.width()/2):0;max=pointer.hasClass('low')?parseFloat(self.highPointer.css("left"))+(self.highPointer.width()/2):self.domNode.width();}
var value=Math.min(Math.max(position,min),max);self.setPosition(pointer,value,true);},setPosition:function(pointer,position,isPx,animate){var leftPos,rightPos,lowPos=parseFloat(this.lowPointer.css("left")),highPos=parseFloat(this.highPointer.css("left"))||0,circleWidth=this.highPointer.width()/2;if(!isPx){position=this.prcToPx(position);}
if(this.options.snap){var expPos=this.correctPositionForSnap(position);if(expPos===-1){return;}else{position=expPos;}}
if(pointer[0]===this.highPointer[0]){highPos=Math.round(position-circleWidth);}else{lowPos=Math.round(position-circleWidth);}
pointer[animate?'animate':'css']({'left':Math.round(position-circleWidth)});if(this.isSingle()){leftPos=0;}else{leftPos=lowPos+circleWidth;rightPos=highPos+circleWidth;}
var w=Math.round(highPos+circleWidth-leftPos);this.bar[animate?'animate':'css']({'width':Math.abs(w),'left':(w>0)?leftPos:leftPos+w});this.showPointerValue(pointer,position,animate);this.isReadonly();},correctPositionForSnap:function(position){var currentValue=this.positionToValue(position)-this.options.from;var diff=this.options.width/(this.interval/this.options.step),expectedPosition=(currentValue/this.options.step)*diff;if(position<=expectedPosition+diff/2&&position>=expectedPosition-diff/2){return expectedPosition;}else{return-1;}},setValue:function(value){var values=value.toString().split(',');values[0]=Math.min(Math.max(values[0],this.options.from),this.options.to)+'';if(values.length>1){values[1]=Math.min(Math.max(values[1],this.options.from),this.options.to)+'';}
this.options.value=value;var prc=this.valuesToPrc(values.length===2?values:[0,values[0]]);if(this.isSingle()){this.setPosition(this.highPointer,prc[1]);}else{this.setPosition(this.lowPointer,prc[0]);this.setPosition(this.highPointer,prc[1]);}},renderScale:function(){var s=this.options.scale||[this.options.from,this.options.to];var prc=Math.round((100/(s.length-1))*10)/10;var str='';for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++){str+='<span style="left: '+i*prc+'%">'+(s[i]!='|'?'<ins>'+s[i]+'</ins>':'')+'</span>';}
this.scale.html(str);$('ins',this.scale).each(function(){$(this).css({marginLeft:-$(this).outerWidth()/2});});},getBarWidth:function(){var values=this.options.value.split(',');if(values.length>1){return parseFloat(values[1])-parseFloat(values[0]);}else{return parseFloat(values[0]);}},showPointerValue:function(pointer,position,animate){var label=$('.pointer-label',this.domNode)[pointer.hasClass('low')?'first':'last']();var text;var value=this.positionToValue(position);if($.isFunction(this.options.format)){var type=this.isSingle()?undefined:(pointer.hasClass('low')?'low':'high');text=this.options.format(value,type);}else{text=this.options.format.replace('%s',value);}
var width=label.html(text).width(),left=position-width/2;left=Math.min(Math.max(left,0),this.options.width-width);label[animate?'animate':'css']({left:left});this.setInputValue(pointer,value);},valuesToPrc:function(values){var lowPrc=((parseFloat(values[0])-parseFloat(this.options.from))*100/this.interval),highPrc=((parseFloat(values[1])-parseFloat(this.options.from))*100/this.interval);return[lowPrc,highPrc];},prcToPx:function(prc){return(this.domNode.width()*prc)/100;},isDecimal:function(){return((this.options.value+this.options.from+this.options.to).indexOf(".")===-1)?false:true;},positionToValue:function(pos){var value=(pos/this.domNode.width())*this.interval;value=parseFloat(value,10)+parseFloat(this.options.from,10);if(this.isDecimal()){var final=Math.round(Math.round(value/this.options.step)*this.options.step*100)/100;if(final!==0.0){final=''+final;if(final.indexOf(".")===-1){final=final+".";}
while(final.length-final.indexOf('.')<3){final=final+"0";}}else{final="0.00";}
return final;}else{return Math.round(value/this.options.step)*this.options.step;}},setInputValue:function(pointer,v){if(this.isSingle()){this.options.value=v.toString();}else{var values=this.options.value.split(',');if(pointer.hasClass('low')){this.options.value=v+','+values[1];}else{this.options.value=values[0]+','+v;}}
if(this.inputNode.val()!==this.options.value){this.inputNode.val(this.options.value).trigger('change');this.options.onstatechange.call(this,this.options.value);}},getValue:function(){return this.options.value;},getOptions:function(){return this.options;},getRange:function(){return this.options.from+","+this.options.to;},isReadonly:function(){this.domNode.toggleClass('slider-readonly',this.options.disable);},disable:function(){this.options.disable=true;this.isReadonly();},enable:function(){this.options.disable=false;this.isReadonly();},toggleDisable:function(){this.options.disable=!this.options.disable;this.isReadonly();},updateRange:function(range,value){var values=range.toString().split(',');this.interval=parseInt(values[1])-parseInt(values[0]);if(value){this.setValue(value);}else{this.setValue(this.getValue());}}};var pluginName='jRange';$.fn[pluginName]=function(option){var args=arguments,result;this.each(function(){var $this=$(this),data=$.data(this,'plugin_'+pluginName),options=typeof option==='object'&&option;if(!data){$this.data('plugin_'+pluginName,(data=new jRange(this,options)));$(window).resize(function(){data.setValue(data.getValue());});}
if(typeof option==='string'){result=data[option].apply(data,Array.prototype.slice.call(args,1));}});return result||this;};})(jQuery,window,document);});var initial_form_action=[];if(typeof sminprice==='undefined'){var sminprice=0;}
if(typeof smaxprice==='undefined'){var smaxprice=0;}
function topFilter(o){window.location=$(o).val();}
function doProductSort(v){jQuery.ajax({url:"/ajax/preferences?p=sort&v="+v,success:function(){window.location=document.location.href.replace(/pagina[0-9]+\/?/g,"");}});}
function defaultFilters(){$('.filterslink').on('click',function(){var t=$(this).attr('data-type');$.ajax({url:absolute_store_link+"/ajax/preferences?p=filters&v="+t});$(window).trigger('resize');});}
function fPid(node){var pidv=$(node).prev().val();if(pidv.length>0){var promo_id_url=$(node).attr('data-url')+pidv;window.location.replace(promo_id_url);}}
function addAdvFilters(){$('#filters_content').find('#filters_advanced').on('click',function(e){var t=$(e.target);if(t.hasClass('adv_filter_chk')){var f=$('#filters_advanced').find('#advanced_filter_submit'),afu=f.find('#adv_filter_url'),adv_filters_url=afu.val(),tmp=t.val()+"/";adv_filters_url=adv_filters_url.replace(tmp,"");if(tmp.indexOf('rating-')!==-1){$("[id^='rating-']").prop('checked',false);$("#"+t.val()).prop('checked',true);adv_filters_url=adv_filters_url.replace(new RegExp("rating-[1-5]/"),'');}
var afm=f.find('#adv_filter_manufacturers');if(t.attr('id').substring(0,3)==='man'){tmp=t.val();afm.val(afm.val().replace(tmp+",","").replace(","+tmp,"").replace(tmp,""));}
if(t.is(':checked')){if(t.attr('id').substring(0,3)==='man'){afm.val(afm.val().length?afm.val()+","+tmp:tmp);}
else{adv_filters_url+=tmp;}}
afu.val(adv_filters_url);f.fadeIn(animationspeed);hideSubmitButton();}});}
function applyPriceFilter(){var afu=$('#advanced_filter_submit').find('#adv_filter_url'),url=String(afu.val()),sinp=$('#filters_group_adv_price').find('#pricesliderinputs'),minval=sinp.find("#minprice").val(),maxval=sinp.find("#maxprice").val();if(url.indexOf(fpricetok)>-1&&url.indexOf(fpricedelim)>-1){var ra=new RegExp(fpricetok+"[0-9]+"+fpricedelim+"[0-9]+","i");url=url.replace(ra,fpricetok+minval+fpricedelim+maxval);}
else{url=url+fpricetok+minval+fpricedelim+maxval+'/';}
if(minval===sminprice&&maxval===smaxprice){var rc=new RegExp(fpricetok+"[0-9]+"+fpricedelim+"[0-9]+/","i");url=url.replace(rc,"");}
afu.val(url);}
function sanitizePriceRange(){var sinp=$('#filters_group_adv_price').find('#pricesliderinputs'),emin=sinp.find('#minprice'),emax=sinp.find('#maxprice'),vmin=Math.abs(parseInt(emin.val())),vmax=Math.abs(parseInt(emax.val()));emin.val((isNaN(vmin)||vmin<sminprice)?sminprice:vmin);emax.val((isNaN(vmax)||vmax>smaxprice)?smaxprice:vmax);vmin=Math.abs(parseInt(emin.val()));vmax=Math.abs(parseInt(emax.val()));if(vmax<vmin){emax.val(vmin);}}
function setPriceRange(){var vmin=Math.abs(parseInt($('#minprice').val())),vmax=Math.abs(parseInt($('#maxprice').val())),p=$('#filters_group_adv_price').find('#priceslider');if((vmin<vmax&&vmin>=sminprice&&vmin<=smaxprice)||(vmax>vmin&&vmax<=smaxprice&&smaxprice>=sminprice)){p.val(vmin+','+vmax);p.jRange('setValue',$('#priceslider').val());}}
function applyFilters(){var f=$('#filters_advanced').find('#advanced_filter_submit'),aff=f.find('#adv_filter_form'),afm=aff.find('#adv_filter_manufacturers').val(),action=aff.attr('action'),affv=$('#adv_filter_url').val();if(!empty(action)&&action.charAt(action.length-1)!=="/"){action+="/";}
if(!empty(affv)||!empty(afm)){var filtre=empty(affv)?'/':(!empty(afm)&&afm.length>1?'/':'')+'filtre/';action+=afm+filtre+affv;window.location.href=action;}
else if(isID('filters_adv_remove')&&$('#filters_advanced').find('input[type="checkbox"]:checked').length===0){window.location.href=$('#filters_adv_remove').attr('href');}
aff.on('submit',function(e){return false;});}
function advFiltSearch(){var action=$('#adv_filter_form').attr('action'),affv=$('#adv_filter_url').val();if(!empty(action)&&action.charAt(action.length-1)!=="/"){action+="/";}
var afm=$('#adv_filter_manufacturers').val(),filtre=empty(affv)?'/':(!empty(afm)&&afm.length>1?'/':'')+'filtre/';action+=afm+filtre+affv;if(!empty(action)){initial_form_action=action.split('/');}}
function hideSubmitButton(){var fc=$('#filters_advanced').find('#advanced_filter_submit'),action=$('#adv_filter_form').attr('action'),affv=$('#adv_filter_url').val();if(!empty(action)&&action.charAt(action.length-1)!=="/"){action+="/";}
var afm=fc.find('#adv_filter_manufacturers').val(),filtre=empty(affv)?'/':(!empty(afm)&&afm.length>1?'/':'')+'filtre/';action+=afm+filtre+affv;var check_action=action.split('/'),all_the_same=!(initial_form_action<check_action||check_action<initial_form_action);all_the_same?fc.fadeOut(animationspeed):fc.fadeIn(animationspeed);}
function sanitizeCompareCheckboxes(){var lr=$('#category_container').find('#category_content');lr.find('.compare_add').each(function(){var tid=$(this).attr('data-id');if(!isID('cbr_'+tid)){lr.find('input[data-id="'+tid+'"]').prop('checked',false).end().find('label[for="compara_'+tid+'"]').find('span').text($.i18n._('compare_add'));}});$('#compare_box_content').find('.comp_remove').each(function(){var tid=$(this).attr('data-id'),c=lr.find('#compara_'+tid);if(isID('compara_'+tid)&&!c.is(':checked')){c.prop('checked',true);lr.find('label[data-prod="'+tid+'"]').find('span').text($.i18n._('compare_remove'));}});}
function gbChoose(id){var l=$('#gb_item_label_'+id),c=$('#gb_item_ch_'+id),chc=$('.gb_choose:checked');l.text(c.is(':checked')?$.i18n._('bundle_remove'):$.i18n._('bundle_add'));if(chc.length===0){$('#gb_total_price').text('0');$('#gb_discount').text('0');$('#gb_final_price').text('0');}
else{var d='gbid='+$('#gbundle_items').attr('data-gbid')+'&'+chc.serialize();$.ajax({type:'POST',url:absolute_store_link+'/ajax/promo_gbundle_price',data:d}).done(function(res){if(res.length<200){var p=res.split('|');$('#gb_total_price').text(p[0]);$('#gb_discount').text(p[1]);$('#gb_final_price').text(p[2]);}});}}
function gb_addtocart(){var chc=$('.gb_choose:checked');if(chc.length===0){alert($.i18n._('select_bundle'));}
else{var gb_form='<form id="gb_form" action="'+(store_ssl_link?store_ssl_link:absolute_store_link)+'/adaugaincos-0/" method="POST">';chc.each(function(){gb_form+='<input type="hidden" name="product-'+$(this).val()+'" value="1">';});gb_form+='</form>';$('body').append(gb_form);$('#gb_form').submit();}}
function gridList(ltype){ltype=ltype||'grid';var ntype=ltype==='grid'?'list':'grid',g=$('#grid'),l=$('#list'),w=$('#wrapper_listing_products'),lp=w.find('.product_box_parent');w.removeClass('listing_'+ntype).addClass('listing_'+ltype);$.ajax({url:absolute_store_link+"/ajax/preferences?p=listing&v="+ltype});if(ltype==='grid'){l.removeClass('list_on').addClass('list_off');g.removeClass('grid_off').addClass('grid_on');w.hasClass('listing_gen')?lp.addClass('col-xs-24 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 col-xl-4 col-xxl-3'):lp.addClass('col-xs-24 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 col-xxl-4');}else{g.removeClass('grid_on').addClass('grid_off');l.removeClass('list_off').addClass('list_on');w.hasClass('listing_gen')?lp.removeClass('col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 col-xl-4 col-xxl-3').addClass('col-xs-24'):lp.removeClass('col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-6 col-xxl-4').addClass('col-xs-24');}
$(window).trigger('resize');}
function wResize(){if(isID('advanced_filter_submit')){hideSubmitButton();rhideSubmitButton();}
setColumns();}
function hideSliderButton(){if($('#filters_advanced input:checked').length===0){$('#advanced_filter_submit').fadeOut(animationspeed);}}
function listingSlider(){var slc=$('#filters_advanced').find('#filters_group_adv_price'),sinp=slc.find('#pricesliderinputs'),smin=sinp.find("#minprice"),smax=sinp.find("#maxprice"),pricelider=slc.find("#priceslider");pricelider.jRange({from:sminprice,to:smaxprice,step:1,isRange:true,showLabels:true,showScale:false,format:'%s '+homecurrency,width:192,onstatechange:function(){var nmin=parseInt($('.pointer-label.low').text()),nmax=parseInt($('.pointer-label.high').text());smin.val(nmin);smax.val(nmax);if(nmin!=sminsetprice||nmax!==smaxsetprice){applyPriceFilter();hideSubmitButton();}
else{hideSliderButton();}},ondragend:function(){var nmin=parseInt($('.pointer-label.low').text()),nmax=parseInt($('.pointer-label.high').text());smin.val(nmin);smax.val(nmax);if(nmin!=sminsetprice||nmax!==smaxsetprice){applyPriceFilter();hideSubmitButton();}
else{hideSliderButton();}}});}
function setColumns(){if(window.matchMedia("(min-width: 768px)").matches){columnEqualHeights($('.product_box_parent, .product_b_container'),false);columnEqualHeights($('.product_box_name'),false);}
else{$('.product_box_container').css('height','auto');$('.product_box_name').find('a').css('height','auto');}}
$(document).ready(function(){$('body').on('change','#sortsel',function(){doProductSort(jQuery(this).val());}).on('click','input[id^="gb_item_ch_"]',function(){gbChoose($(this).attr('id').substr(11));}).livequery(function(){if(isID('compare_box')&&!$('#compare_box').hasClass('hidden')){$('.olark-launch-button-wrapper').addClass('with_compare');}});fScrollbar();if(isID('filters_standard')||isID('man_filters')||isID('filters_content')){accordion($('#filters').find('.accordion'),false,400);}
if(isID('filters')){tabs($('#filters').find('#filters_content'));}
if(isID('adv_filter_form')){addAdvFilters();advFiltSearch();defaultFilters();}
$(".pricein").each(function(){$(this).on({keypress:function(e){return isNumberKey(e);},blur:function(){setPriceRange();sanitizePriceRange();applyPriceFilter();hideSubmitButton();},keyup:function(){$('#advanced_filter_submit').fadeIn(animationspeed);}});});setColumns();$(window).on('resize',wResize);if(isID('filters_group_adv_price')){listingSlider();}});
  </script>

     (Mac) și folosește bara de căutare.
    </span>
   </span>
  </div>

             <div class="clearfix" id="category_cdescription">
              <h2>
               Care sunt avantajele unui ultrabook?
              </h2>
              <p class="clearfix">
               Un ultrabook iti ofera doua beneficii importante: design compact si performante de top. Perioada in care consideram ca laptopurile sunt mai slabe decat PC-urile s-a incheiat deja, acestea avand procesoare foarte performante si tot felul de tehnologii care rivalizeaza cu variantele desktop. Desi suntem tentati sa afirmam ca un ultrabook este mult mai scump decat un PC cu aceleasi performante, sa nu uitam un aspect important: in cazul unui ultrabook primesti la pachet si un display, o tastatura si daca te descurci bine cu touch pad-ul, chiar si un mouse. Si bineinteles, portabilitatea. Oricat de performant ar fi un PC, nu il poti baga rapid in geanta in cazul in care vrei sa te joci, sa lucrezi sau sa te uiti la filme in alta locatie.
              </p>
              <ul>
               <li>
                <h3>
                 Cum alegi ultrabook-ul ideal?
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Pentru a te ajuta sa faci o alegere potrivita, ti-am pregatit acest ghid in care iti prezentam ce specificatii ar trebui sa ai in vedere daca vrei sa-ti cumperi un ultrabook cu un raport pret-performanta cat mai bun:
                </p>
                <p>
                 - Un
                 <strong>
                  procesor
                 </strong>
                 de generatie cat mai noua, bine pregatit pentru viitor, cu o arhitectura eficienta. Acest lucru este necesar pentru o autonomie cat mai buna, o caracteristica importanta a ultrabook-urilor.
                </p>
                <p>
                 - Suficienta
                 <strong>
                  memorie RAM
                 </strong>
                 - un minim de 16GB RAM ar fi ideal pentru a te bucura de o configuratie performanta. Daca este vorba de un workstation insa, ar fi o idee mai buna sa mergi pe varianta de 32GB RAM.
                </p>
                <p>
                 -
                 <strong>
                  Stocare
                 </strong>
                 rapida de tip
                 <strong>
                  SSD
                 </strong>
                 - un minim necesar ar fi de 512 GB sau 1 TB, dar nu uita sa iei in considerare si varianta unui upgrade pe viitor cu ajutorul unui slot M.2.
                </p>
                <p>
                 - Un
                 <strong>
                  sistem de racire
                 </strong>
                 eficient, capabil sa tina temperaturile sub control atunci cand este utilizat intens, chiar si pe timp de canicula. In acelasi timp, este important ca acesta sa fie suficient de silentios sau chiar sa functioneze fanless in contextul unei utilizari de baza (browsing, text editing, chat, etc.)
                </p>
                <p>
                 - Un
                 <strong>
                  display
                 </strong>
                 care poate reproduce bine culorile si care poate afisa o rezolutie cel putin echivalenta cu FHD sau chiar 2K sau 4K. Ultrabook-urile ies in evidenta si prin optiunea de
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/ultrabook/filtre/display-touchscreen-da/">
                  touchscreen
                 </a>
                 , sau chiar ecrane secundare - cum este cazul anumitor modele ASUS din seria
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/ultrabook/asus/filtre/model-platforma-zenbook/">
                  ZenBook
                 </a>
                 .
                </p>
                <p>
                 - Multiple
                 <strong>
                  optiuni de personalizare
                 </strong>
                 - cum ar fi iluminarea pentru tastatura, culori speciale pentru carcasa, senzor de amprenta, sau posibilitatea de transformare in tableta prin rabatarea ecranului, cum este cazul variantelor
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/ultrabook/filtre/model-2-in-1-da/">
                  2-in-1
                 </a>
                 .
                </p>
               </li>
               <li>
                <h3>
                 Ce ar trebui sa cumperi impreuna cu un ultrabook?
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Fie ca vorbim despre activitati simple multimedia, office, sau productivitate avansata, pe langa ultrabook ai nevoie si de alte accesorii: in primul rand, un
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/mouse/filtre/general-tip-mouse-wireless/">
                  mouse
                 </a>
                 (daca nu vrei sa lucrezi exclusiv cu touch pad-ul). Daca planuiesti sa stai mai mult la birou si o
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/tastaturi/filtre/general-tehnologie-wireless/">
                  tastatura wireless
                 </a>
                 ar fi ideala pentru tine. Si bineinteles, nu uita de transport. O
                 <a href="https://www.pcgarage.ro/genti-notebook/">
                  geanta sau un rucsac
                 </a>
                 ar trebui sa fie nelipsite din wishlist-ul tau atunci cand cauti un ultrabook nou.
                </p>
               </li>
              </ul>
             </div>
             <div class="mt-3">

             </p>

              Conditii comerciale Ultrabook
             </p>

              </li>
              <li>
               Informatiile prezentate in aceasta pagina (categoria Ultrabook) au caracter informativ si pot fi modificate de catre vanzator fara o anuntare prealabila.
              </li>
             </ul>
